; Issue: https://github.com/rustledger/rustledger/issues/273
; Description: Inventory lots with same price but different dates
; Expected: No errors - lots with same price but different dates should be distinct

2025-01-01 open Assets:Abc ABC
2025-01-01 open Assets:Cash
2025-01-01 open Equity:Opening

; Create two lots with same price but different dates
2026-01-01 * "Buy with explicit date"
  Assets:Abc                       2 ABC {10.01 USD, 2018-12-06}
  Assets:Abc                       1 ABC {10.01 USD}
  Equity:Opening

; Sell both lots - one has explicit date, one doesn't
2026-01-03 * "Sell"
  Assets:Abc                      -2 ABC {10.01 USD, 2018-12-06}
  Assets:Abc                      -1 ABC {10.01 USD}
  Assets:Cash                  30.03 USD

; Balance should be zero after selling all
2026-01-04 balance Assets:Abc      0 ABC
